1
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:10,080
All our sorrows.

2
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:48,759
Miss Gu.

3
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:49,720
Lord Jian.

4
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,280
Visiting so late at night,

5
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:52,340
please forgive me.

6
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,060
Please come in.

7
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:05,820
Please sit.

8
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,840
What brings you here?

9
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:16,480
Lord Jian,

10
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:19,450
I want to ask you about someone.

11
00:02:21,079 --> 00:02:22,880
The person you want to ask about,

12
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,800
is it Lord Su Ziliang?

13
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:27,490
Exactly.

14
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:31,040
Lord Su once told me

15
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:35,020
he would leave that jade pendant you're wearing as a token.

16
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,840
If I'm not mistaken,

17
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,880
you are his daughter.

18
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:45,640
Yes.

19
00:02:47,079 --> 00:02:49,560
I am his eldest daughter, Su Zhaoxue.

20
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:05,320
Inside the jade pendant my father left,

21
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:06,250
there was a note.

22
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,280
It said,

23
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:09,700
'If in trouble,

24
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:10,920
seek you out.'

25
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,400
I naturally trust my father.

26
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:20,040
But...

27
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,730
Back then, we followed Lord Su,

28
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:31,810
assisting His Majesty,

29
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,520
rooting out evil,

30
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:35,380
and bringing peace to the people.

31
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:38,560
I never expected him to end up like that.

32
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:40,760
Lord Su used to say,

33
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:44,020
'If I cannot protect the people's lives,

34
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:47,220
what does it matter if my robes are stained with blood?'

35
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:48,960
So,

36
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:53,240
when disaster struck, he ordered me to save myself

37
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,900
and wait for the right moment.

38
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:58,960
To seize the chance to catch those corrupt officials harming the people

39
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,660
and bring them all to justice.

40
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:03,840
Even until his death,

41
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:08,240
my father was still thinking of the people.

42
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:12,210
To have such a good official

43
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,360
is truly the country's fortune,

44
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,779
and the people's fortune.

45
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:24,560
Miss Su,

46
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:27,960
I am now part of this game.

47
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:29,280
My hands are tied.

48
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:32,840
But I, Jian Boning, swear on my life,

49
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:35,600
I have never been disloyal to Lord Su.

50
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:41,159
Please, Miss Su, you must believe me.

51
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,880
Where is the second miss, Su Qingyan, now?

52
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:56,850
You've seen her.

53
00:04:58,040 --> 00:05:01,300
Last time, when you went to Min Huishi's house with Fang Ji,

54
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:04,320
the girl standing next to me was Qingyan.

55
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,040
You must take her and leave immediately.

56
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,500
Go as far away as possible.

57
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:13,320
You must not get involved in this case again.

58
00:05:13,320 --> 00:05:14,050
Impossible.

59
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:17,120
I will absolutely not leave.

60
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:20,880
Back then, my father was ordered to investigate the witchcraft case.

61
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:22,680
It was after he entered the palace to collect evidence

62
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,840
that he was framed.

63
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:26,240
Lord Jian,

64
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,060
is the current case

65
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:30,680
related to the witchcraft case from back then?

66
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:34,240
Otherwise, why would Lu Shen mention that incident in the palace?

67
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:36,040
Actually, I have long suspected

68
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:38,940
that today's witchcraft case

69
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:41,040
and the one from back then

70
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,210
share the same mastermind.

71
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:47,290
Those suspects who were silenced,

72
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:51,200
their deaths were very similar to those of the victims back then.

73
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:53,240
So I surmise,

74
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:56,240
although Lord Su died unjustly,

75
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:59,500
he also thwarted the mastermind's plot.

76
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:01,400
That is why, ten years later,

77
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:05,120
they are using witchcraft to commit crimes again.

78
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:09,320
My father's wish was to uphold justice for the people.

79
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:13,130
To never let corrupt officials plague the world.

80
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:15,980
Since he told me to find you...

81
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:18,680
He must have trusted that you could help me.

82
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,760
I must clear my father's name.

83
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:25,440
I have been secretly investigating all these years.

84
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:28,400
Back then, Lord Su gave the evidence of the witchcraft case...

85
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:29,860
...to a man of the Jianghu.

86
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:33,520
This man has been wanted by the Imperial Court for years.

87
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:36,050
Now, he is entrenched by the river in Jinzhou.

88
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:38,760
But he is elusive.

89
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,780
I have never been able to find him.

90
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:45,159
What is his name?

91
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:47,180
Zhou Laohu.

92
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:49,080
It is said...

93
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:51,000
...that Zhou Laohu often abducts women.

94
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,120
He has a peculiar habit.

95
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,920
He orders the abducted women...

96
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:55,600
...to be locked in a red sedan chair,

97
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,400
and collects them late at night.

98
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:09,940
Zhou Laohu is a water bandit who has evaded the Court for years.

99
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:12,240
It won't be easy to find him.

100
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:15,210
Let's start with this red sedan chair.

101
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:16,640
Wait.

102
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,180
Someone is crying.

103
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:23,040
Miss.

104
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:33,360
Miss.

105
00:07:34,159 --> 00:07:34,960
What's wrong?

106
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,040
Who are you?

107
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:38,240
I don't want to marry a water bandit.

108
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,600
I don't want to marry a water bandit.

109
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,480
I beg you.

110
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,360
Don't be afraid.

111
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,220
We mean no harm.

112
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:45,800
Is the water bandit you speak of Zhou Laohu?

113
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:56,800
Did your parents force you to marry him?

114
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:03,720
My parents and family died early.

115
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:08,560
You two must be from out of town.

116
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,940
You should leave quickly.

117
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:11,740
Go, now.

118
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:15,960
Recently, Zhou Laohu has been running rampant in the Jianghu.

119
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:17,760
Now he is passing through here.

120
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:22,720
It's one thing to rob merchant ships and fishing boats.

121
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:26,720
But if any family has a pretty daughter,

122
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,440
he will snatch her back to his stronghold

123
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:30,480
to be his wife.

124
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,679
But I am just a blind girl.

125
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:36,200
Yet he still chose me.

126
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:37,320
I refused.

127
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:40,760
So the locals seized me and brought me here.

128
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,880
Waiting for Zhou Laohu to collect me.

129
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:45,140
Don't be afraid, Miss.

130
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:45,980
We are here.

131
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,640
Unless he's the King of Heaven himself,

132
00:08:47,640 --> 00:08:48,970
we are not afraid of him.

133
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:52,440
Are you two officials?

134
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:55,760
Uh...

135
00:08:56,840 --> 00:09:00,120
We are government clerks and scribes, just passing by.

136
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:04,690
You shouldn't invite trouble for my sake.

137
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:08,780
The local authorities can't do anything about him.

138
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:12,010
Miss, do you know...

139
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,840
...where that red sedan chair...

140
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:15,040
...usually appears?

141
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:18,280
Late at night,

142
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:21,600
the red sedan chair will appear on the lake.

143
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:29,520
Miss.

144
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,380
Don't be afraid, Miss.

145
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:32,930
We'll take you home in a bit.

146
00:09:33,520 --> 00:09:35,850
I'll take your place as the bride tonight.

147
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:36,360
No.

148
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:43,400
It's too suspicious. You can't go.

149
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:45,330
It's too suspicious. You can't go.

150
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,000
Little beauty.

151
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,080
Surprise!

152
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:43,720
What are you doing here?

153
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:44,920
Stop fooling around.

154
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:45,960
Go back, quickly.

155
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:53,010
It's so full.

156
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,040
Apples?

157
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:03,900
Give them back.

158
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:17,980
I was just thinking...

159
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:20,080
If that Zhou the Tiger

160
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:23,120
tries to snatch a bride but snatches a man instead,

161
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:25,800
his reaction will be hilarious.

162
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:27,180
I don't want to miss it.

163
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:29,200
You're just making trouble.

164
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:29,800
Nonsense.

165
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:32,050
How am I making trouble?

166
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,480
I've left a mark.

167
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:35,660
The Little Marquis will find us soon.

168
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:38,220
He doesn't need me to lead the way.

169
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:39,800
Dying alone

170
00:11:40,760 --> 00:11:43,240
is not as good as dying together.

171
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,240
If anything happens,

172
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:49,440
What's wrong?

173
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:58,920
at least we'll have company on the road to the underworld.

174
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,000
Get up.

175
00:12:38,920 --> 00:12:39,720
Brother Fang!

176
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:40,760
Brother Fang!

177
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:45,560
Miss Su.

178
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:47,560
Miss Su!

179
00:12:48,560 --> 00:12:49,420
Did he hurt you?

180
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:50,040
No.

181
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:51,320
Good.

182
00:12:54,760 --> 00:12:55,560
Brother Jian.

183
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:56,840
Brother Fang.

184
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,370
How did you find this place?

185
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:04,330
Lord Jian was afraid we were in danger,

186
00:13:04,760 --> 00:13:06,360
so he followed us all the way.

187
00:13:08,560 --> 00:13:09,360
Brother Jian,

188
00:13:09,400 --> 00:13:10,920
did you see the people who kidnapped us last night?

189
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:11,320
No.

190
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:12,500
Last night,

191
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:15,200
I saw them carry the sedan chair into this stronghold.

192
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,880
But there were too many guards outside,

193
00:13:16,880 --> 00:13:19,680
so I had to wait until now for a chance to rescue you.

194
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:23,540
Did you see Zhou the Tiger?

195
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:28,480
We got into a sedan chair yesterday,

196
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:30,330
and fainted shortly after.

197
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:32,800
Strange.

198
00:13:33,880 --> 00:13:35,760
There's no one outside the stronghold now.

199
00:13:35,760 --> 00:13:36,420
It's empty.

200
00:13:38,520 --> 00:13:38,920
Oh no.

201
00:13:49,760 --> 00:13:52,290
I knew there was something wrong with you two.

202
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:54,520
I wanted to interrogate you properly.

203
00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:57,920
Now I've caught you red-handed.

204
00:13:59,160 --> 00:14:00,090
What do you mean?

205
00:14:02,880 --> 00:14:03,480
Lord Jian.

206
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:05,480
What do you think?

207
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:07,580
How could I have missed it?

208
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:10,000
The legendary elusive

209
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:13,080
Zhou the Tiger, wanted by the court for years,

210
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:16,040
is actually you, Qingniang.

211
00:14:18,040 --> 00:14:18,700
Qingniang?

212
00:14:19,560 --> 00:14:22,290
I've been looking so hard for you all these years.

213
00:14:23,880 --> 00:14:24,840
Looking for me?

214
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:28,900
You wanted to kill me, didn't you?

215
00:14:29,120 --> 00:14:31,000
You ungrateful wretch!

216
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,440
I'll make you pay for Lord Su's death!

217
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:33,440
Qingniang, wait!

218
00:14:33,920 --> 00:14:35,380
It's a misunderstanding!

219
00:14:36,400 --> 00:14:37,200
This sword...

220
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:40,650
Are you Sister Song,

221
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:45,120
who plotted with my father in the study?

222
00:14:48,520 --> 00:14:49,480
You are...

223
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:52,560
She is Lord Su Ziliang's eldest daughter,

224
00:14:52,560 --> 00:14:53,220
Su Zhaoxue.

225
00:14:58,440 --> 00:15:01,120
You are Miss Zhaoxue?

226
00:15:02,560 --> 00:15:03,880
It's me.

227
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:05,840
Let me look at you.

228
00:15:08,400 --> 00:15:09,530
You've grown so big.

229
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:11,960
Zhaoxue.

230
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:12,440
Stop!

231
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:14,640
She really is Su Zhaoxue!

232
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:15,500
Qingniang,

233
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:17,160
put down the sword!

234
00:15:17,160 --> 00:15:18,360
Don't hurt Miss Su.

235
00:15:18,800 --> 00:15:19,860
Put down the sword!

236
00:15:22,120 --> 00:15:25,320
Back then, all the female members of the Su family were sold off.

237
00:15:25,320 --> 00:15:28,320
She bears some resemblance to the young Miss Su.

238
00:15:28,720 --> 00:15:31,320
But there is no official brand on her forehead.

239
00:15:42,680 --> 00:15:44,960
A glance at the misty rain, a fleeting dream.
